{
  "stem": "21494.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then-- then come-- start to come the potatoes to take out, and other work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then they come to take workers from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were happy to go out a little bit from the ghetto, to be free a little bit, to eat something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then they held-- I told you, the [NON-ENGLISH] was a countess [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] made business with my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she know it very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But she disappeared when the Russians come, or maybe they arrested.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what was with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But the manager [INAUDIBLE], I don't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He came to the ghetto to ask for workers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But he say, I would like workers, but I want David's, which was killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I know, the children, the family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This was a big, big favor to take out from the ghetto people to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It means already that you can run out to save yourself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father-- I told you, he was killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took him out from the basement in a wagon, and they killed him, and they took him to the cemetery where horses and dogs were buried.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He and two more Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know who killed him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I'll tell you after the war what I did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I took-- I took this revenge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will tell you something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our Judenrat was very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tried their best.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But sometimes they needed something to do, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then they didn't have very difficult, because it was the Fogel, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But later on, when came already the liquidation of the ghetto, he took two girls, a sister is in Detroit, to her sisters.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to cook for him and her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He hided them on their--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Attic.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
